Package: promptbook
Title: Documented, Reproducible, Reusable Data Annotation with LLMs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Roar", "Bakken Stovner", , "robast@oslomet.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Define coding instruments as structured YAML promptbooks and apply
    them to datasets using large language models via 'ellmer'. Supports
    categorical, numeric, boolean, text, and object variable types with
    per-variable model dispatch and automatic variable grouping.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
